05:36.086 --> 05:38.379
I know what this is.

05:38.421 --> 05:41.175
You've got a secret admirer!

05:41.216 --> 05:44.928
[squeals and whoops]

05:46.054 --> 05:49.183
♪♪

05:49.224 --> 05:52.393
[Spike] Ah! Another

05:49.224 --> 05:52.393
Hearts and Hooves Day.

05:52.435 --> 05:54.188
Love is in the air, Discord.

05:54.229 --> 05:56.397
Look at all these happy couples.

05:56.439 --> 05:58.108
How can they be happy if

05:56.439 --> 05:58.108
