06:06.325 --> 06:09.410
I love you, dear, my

06:06.325 --> 06:09.410
sweet, sweet Rari--"

06:09.452 --> 06:11.246
Are you even listening?

06:11.288 --> 06:12.914
Of course.

06:12.956 --> 06:16.043
"Love is something-something,

06:12.956 --> 06:16.043
and Discord is great."

06:16.084 --> 06:17.336
I don't know.

06:17.376 --> 06:19.420
Can we play O & O now?

06:19.462 --> 06:22.090
Sure, after you admit you

06:19.462 --> 06:22.090
