06:22.132 --> 06:23.382
Sugarbelle!

06:26.553 --> 06:28.222
Big Mac's girlfriend.

06:28.263 --> 06:30.891
What's she doing

06:28.263 --> 06:30.891
in town so early?

06:30.932 --> 06:35.354
Well, Sugar Belle, I'm sure

06:30.932 --> 06:35.354
Big Mac won't be expecting it.

06:35.394 --> 06:37.064
[gasp]

06:37.105 --> 06:39.440
She's planning her own

06:37.105 --> 06:39.440
romantic surprise for Big Mac?

06:39.482 --> 06:40.817
What if she goes to

06:39.482 --> 06:40.817
Sweet Apple Acres

06:40.859 --> 06:42.694
before Big Mac's ready

06:40.859 --> 06:42.694
with his surprise?

06:42.736 --> 06:43.904
We've got to warn him!

06:45.155 --> 06:45.947
[zap]

06:46.865 --> 06:47.866
[zap]

06:47.908 --> 06:49.450
Whoa! [clang]

06:49.492 --> 06:50.451
Whoa!

06:50.493 --> 06:54.915
Mig Back! Mig Back!

06:54.956 --> 06:57.458
