07:02.881 --> 07:05.217
You gotta keep her away from

07:02.881 --> 07:05.217
here until the barn's finished!

07:05.717 --> 07:06.551
Eyup!

07:08.970 --> 07:10.889
I wonder what she

07:08.970 --> 07:10.889
