07:10.931 --> 07:13.850
[chuckle] We don't

07:10.931 --> 07:13.850
have to wonder.

07:13.892 --> 07:15.476
[snap]

07:15.518 --> 07:16.436
Agh!

07:18.188 --> 07:20.481
Will you warn me next

07:18.188 --> 07:20.481
