07:20.523 --> 07:27.447
♪♪

07:29.532 --> 07:31.952
Oh, she hasn't seen him yet.

07:31.993 --> 07:33.494
Take note, Discord.

07:33.536 --> 07:35.705
This is what love is all about!

07:37.707 --> 07:41.420
Spike, "Love is about

07:37.707 --> 07:41.420
spying in the bushes."

