Make fun of me

07:41.461 --> 07:42.963
all you want,

07:43.004 --> 07:44.505
but look at

07:43.004 --> 07:44.505
Big Mac's face

07:44.547 --> 07:46.049
and tell me you don't

07:44.547 --> 07:46.049
believe in love.

07:49.636 --> 07:51.430
[chuckle]

07:51.471 --> 07:53.265
I hope he'll be

07:51.471 --> 07:53.265
