[whimper]

07:57.936 --> 07:59.187
Oh, hey.

07:59.229 --> 08:00.063
We're just...

08:00.105 --> 08:00.981
not spying.

08:01.022 --> 08:01.982
Hush!

08:04.776 --> 08:07.528
I mean, he has been

08:04.776 --> 08:07.528
