08:07.570 --> 08:10.531
so he'll be fine, right?

08:10.573 --> 08:11.699
[sigh]

08:11.741 --> 08:13.785
How should I tell

08:11.741 --> 08:13.785
Big Mac tonight?

08:13.827 --> 08:16.621
"You won't need to come visit

08:13.827 --> 08:16.621
