09:32.155 --> 09:34.241
Oh, I hate seeing you

09:32.155 --> 09:34.241
like this, Big Mac,

09:34.282 --> 09:36.617
and over a

09:34.282 --> 09:36.617
girl, no less.

09:36.659 --> 09:41.622
I'm calling an emergency Guys'

09:36.659 --> 09:41.622
Night right now to cheer you up.

09:41.664 --> 09:44.625
[honk]

09:44.667 --> 09:47.628
Besides, we can't have

09:44.667 --> 09:47.628
you ruining any more of my

09:47.670 --> 09:50.673
1000-year-old monogrammed

09:47.670 --> 09:50.673
handkerchiefs.

